                                                Based on the above risk profile we will implement the appropriate
                                                investment strategy, monitoring Your investments amd respond quickly and
                                                flexible to market changes.
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="crypto-overview-gallery-item item5">
                                <div class="hover panel">
                                    <div class="front">
                                        <div class="side1">
                                            <h5>We provide</h5>
                                            <p>You a solution where You take the investment decision with the support of
                                                our investment specialists</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="back">
                                        <div class="side2">
                                            <p>Together we analyse Your individual situation by focusing on:<br>
                                                &bull; Your risk appetite<br>
                                                &bull; Your return expectations<br>
                                                &bull; Your investment goal<br>
                                                &bull; Your investment horizon<br>
                                                &bull; The structure of Your actual wealth<br>
                                                Based on the above risk profile we will implement the appropriate
                                                investment strategy, monitoring Your investments amd respond quickly and
                                                flexible to market changes.
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="dashboard-footer">
        <div class="support-block">
            <div class="support-block-bg"></div>
            <div class="support-block-subtitle animate-visible"><b>Do you have any Question?</b></div>
            <div class="support-block-title animate-visible"><h2>Contact Your Account Manager</h2></div>
            <div class="support-block-description animate-visible"><h5>Please, click to Request Button and your Personal
                    Manager call to your phone imidiallity.</h5></div>
            <div class="support-block-link animate-visible">
                <a onclick='$("#zsiq_agtpic").click();' class="btn btn_lg">Send Request <span class="hidden-arrow-right"></span></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
{% endblock %}

{% block javascripts %}
    {{ parent() }}
    <script src="{{ asset('js/pages/myproducts.min.js') }}"></script>
{% endblock %}
